    </dt>
    <dd>The name of the Azure Maps Account. Changing this forces a new resource to be created.
</dd>

    <dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span>Primary<wbr>Access<wbr>Key</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type"><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/language-reference/builtin-types/built-in-types">string</a></span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The primary key used to authenticate and authorize access to the Maps REST APIs.
</dd>

    <dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span>Resource<wbr>Group<wbr>Name</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type"><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/language-reference/builtin-types/built-in-types">string</a></span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The name of the Resource Group in which the Azure Maps Account should exist. Changing this forces a new resource to be created.
</dd>

    <dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">

        <span class="property-indicator"></span>

</dd>

    <dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">

        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
